Description_lang: Carrying the mark of Korven the Prime, which grants the ability, Painkiller. Upon taking a blow that would have killed you, instead you are encased in a block of amber, which reduces damage taken and regenerates health and mana for the duration of the spell.This effect cannot occur more than once every 3 min.Only effective at Kypari Zar.
